{"tid":1999502,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone 11pro轉8SE 既人到底咩心態？","createTime":"2020-05-03T08:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T16:39:05.000Z","uid":219147,"like":9,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d84c1029a08cc626745008fc227e27d1fccae645","tid":1999502,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"住開深水灣，搬去深水埗，咪玩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZdKPH-L7V6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZdKPH-L7V6E&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7750b119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZdKPH-L7V6E</a>"},{"pid":"8a85bc8b70065ee430b6fa06bd2e714cb74c8156","tid":1999502,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩問題"},{"pid":"6ff7e7d6bde38c03e559def7b7c100e4ed1d493f","tid":1999502,"uid":111996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"多翻D錢，等多幾個月 賣Se換iphone 12 同人講 我用8好多年了，準備換新機"},{"pid":"2753f3f6e569518bf9ab5262b6bf910d41ca5124","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ff7e7d6bde38c03e559def7b7c100e4ed1d493f","tid":1999502,"uid":111996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"多翻D錢，等多幾個月 賣Se換iphone 12 同人講 我用8好多年了，準備換新機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"我好慳架<br />\n手機用到咪得 追咁貼都冇用"},{"pid":"0ae60d953857c2b93afc1566873f73e1110158e3","tid":1999502,"uid":191588,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"Click view囉，起碼有你幫手宣傳。"},{"pid":"4f591c16a24aa786d946abb9b7b8fd613bc49d06","tid":1999502,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:55:59.000Z","msg":"要威囉"},{"pid":"32091aa23289697f8f91f018ff13b3725e6a7424","tid":1999502,"uid":22422,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"同11(PRO)相同性能 輕身 touch id <br />\n賣咗部嘢買番SE 重慳到幾千蚊"},{"pid":"0dcbe6be3f8558ef44c79a35f6b99bad8fac0507","tid":1999502,"uid":219147,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"睇完條片其他唔講 淨係講以下呢兩樣都知條友厄like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1，鐘意佢有番條邊（雙下巴）比我。究竟有幾on9先可以講得出呢啲說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2，可以當佢（8SE）係細版11pro。聽到我爭啲掉撚咗部11pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8547918c9ede1cf4864f8362edbf73d51c2ce7e","tid":1999502,"uid":105678,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"SE 2係for窮撚，同iphone X當年要出8仔畀個低價選擇出嚟，11pro換SE只有窮撚/傻鳩"},{"pid":"f1e12a48be963d36af5039fa69a937adc4ddf8b8","tid":1999502,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"se1 轉se2 呢？<br />\n我手頭上仲有部android主機"},{"pid":"c46288385d1354ea6e13dd7dac795d14f186d490","tid":1999502,"uid":219147,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f1e12a48be963d36af5039fa69a937adc4ddf8b8","tid":1999502,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"se1 轉se2 呢？<br />\n我手頭上仲有部android主機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:46:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果出哂名乜都慢過人<br />\n原因係佢既商業手段<br />\n以佢既商業作風 簡單啲講叫唧牙膏<br />\n當佢出SE2既時候 佢就比咗個陷阱你哋踩<br />\n以計劃好用12  5.4打冧SE2引你哋再換機<br />\n<br />\n例子：一代ipad鍵盤乜都無又無背光燈根本就完全無吸引力 但其實佢已經計劃好 一代之後就用二代ipad，magic鍵盤打冧自己既一代既產品同用家既使用心情<br />\n等出咗一代ipad 11 再比多個 新一代乜都無鍵盤比用家配搭 當用家上咗船之後 佢就出二代鍵盤打冧你哋<br />\n<br />\n所以你要揀SE2 就要諗清楚以上幾點<br />\n同自己有無甘既定力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b677f6ee00aa530de127dbca92a7562ef9c4ded2","tid":1999502,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e12a48be963d36af5039fa69a937adc4ddf8b8","tid":1999502,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"se1 轉se2 呢？<br />\n我手頭上仲有部android主機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:55:49.000Z","msg":"蘋果有的是時間 <br />\n佢就係知你哋輸不起時間 <br />\n就會急 一急就會成為佢哋既木偶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a7fc2b25dd76f6bf3f6a53dca3b236139c03f5","tid":1999502,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T20:38:44.000Z","msg":"想輕，單手操控得唔得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be15011b8c2c5cfd2e0a4a0246bce6ebca3f59a3","tid":1999502,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b677f6ee00aa530de127dbca92a7562ef9c4ded2","tid":1999502,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1e12a48be963d36af5039fa69a937adc4ddf8b8","tid":1999502,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"se1 轉se2 呢？<br />\n我手頭上仲有部android主機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:55:49.000Z","msg":"蘋果有的是時間 <br />\n佢就係知你哋輸不起時間 <br />\n就會急 一急就會成為佢哋既木偶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"其實我又唔係真係好急，因為我本身主力用android機，部se主要用來做e-banking、網購以及工作需要。<br />\n曾經諗過11/11 pro，但係價錢真係太貴(要256），而家256 SE 都係五千內，啱我心水，等多幾個月就買。<br />\n至於等到12先買我諗不了，雖然到時舊型號會平啲，但係到時會冇咗一款版本(例如本身有62、256、512，出新型號之後就冇咗256，就算512平啲對我來講都係over budget)<br />\n仲有12嘅售價同上年11售價相若，就算係最平嘅版本都貴過256 SE，仲未計新產品推出市面後會系統有唔少問題，至少再等多一年系統先穩定，但係到時又會有新型號，一直loop落去，根本買唔到。"},{"pid":"f0cc79120afe264a720b5b4986ffa46bf97c2e7a","tid":1999502,"uid":174639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:46:36.000Z","msg":"體驗下窮撚生活，下一部再轉返12pro"},{"pid":"ea5c5fa643d553b9429664da735165cdcdbf0b5f","tid":1999502,"uid":298577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"我當年都係iphone6s轉se<br />\n因為想要細mon"},{"pid":"3b7adf817a3fb91546451889ea6b977250396b19","tid":1999502,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"食慣鮑參翅肚想食返茶記"},{"pid":"38c170ff84ce90cd21d747516fa6ada5769e50e1","tid":1999502,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實11 pro 手感已經好好<br />\n<br />\n電又多"},{"pid":"3b3642891ea7248b02e65729317228b1e6714a64","tid":1999502,"uid":215341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:23:52.000Z","msg":"影咩相吖，你最多咪拎嚟影下文件影下snapchat，啲拍攝功能你用得幾多次吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90d0f99a03daa3b951e0abe56ad04d78e5220e5","tid":1999502,"uid":70447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"同一粒u 網細左 鏡頭少左 效能一定快啲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148ad9fb3ce61f9122003aea75c651a35eac042c","tid":1999502,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2753f3f6e569518bf9ab5262b6bf910d41ca5124","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ff7e7d6bde38c03e559def7b7c100e4ed1d493f","tid":1999502,"uid":111996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"多翻D錢，等多幾個月 賣Se換iphone 12 同人講 我用8好多年了，準備換新機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"我好慳架<br />\n手機用到咪得 追咁貼都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:31:01.000Z","msg":"你當初買11pro把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3267abd450d68175ed29cd037ad2b31cd583ec1e","tid":1999502,"uid":211341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:36:30.000Z","msg":"一班保守接受唔到新事物既人但又淨係識得蘋果最好既人。"},{"pid":"e80b4b5303af3304936f00bc9f68ecce3cf7caf6","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148ad9fb3ce61f9122003aea75c651a35eac042c","tid":1999502,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2753f3f6e569518bf9ab5262b6bf910d41ca5124","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ff7e7d6bde38c03e559def7b7c100e4ed1d493f","tid":1999502,"uid":111996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"多翻D錢，等多幾個月 賣Se換iphone 12 同人講 我用8好多年了，準備換新機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"我好慳架<br />\n手機用到咪得 追咁貼都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:31:01.000Z","msg":"你當初買11pro把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"關...關...關你咩事阿<br />\n買部手機洗唔洗問你阿...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b184667431b848a5efa2fab476de474b34c0c2","tid":1999502,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e80b4b5303af3304936f00bc9f68ecce3cf7caf6","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"148ad9fb3ce61f9122003aea75c651a35eac042c","tid":1999502,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2753f3f6e569518bf9ab5262b6bf910d41ca5124","tid":1999502,"uid":78336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"我好慳架<br />\n手機用到咪得 追咁貼都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T01:31:01.000Z","msg":"你當初買11pro把撚啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"關...關...關你咩事阿<br />\n買部手機洗唔洗問你阿...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"用完11pro先話追咁貼冇用，仲話好慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔好同我講你不嬲用平機，無用過11pro啊。咁就文不對題，入黎把撚架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a60607a0b2877e1fb2ec7847a7a4cd7cfa2051","tid":1999502,"uid":64918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"有啲乜嘢大問題?<br />\n<br />\n1. 極度討厭 Face ID. 未戴口罩已經唔係太鍾意, 不過覺得小問題. 戴咗之後好撚大問題. <br />\n<br />\n2. 用返 Home Button 之後先至發覺相差咁遠, Swipe Up 真係唔好用. 好似相差好少, 但係感覺分別好大. 都未計成日唔小心揩到 Bottom Bar.<br />\n<br />\n3. 以前成日覺得要大Mon, 打機睇戲乜都得. 依家個電話基本上 做少好多呢啲嘢. 基本 Whatsapp Twitter, 用啲 Apps 買嘢夠晒. <br />\n<br />\n4. iPhone XR / 11 都還可以, Pro 真係 &quot;重&quot;. <br />\n<br />\nSE 如果可以有埋 Night Mode, 同有辦法提升電量 就 Perfect. 足夠光嘅情況之下影相都冇問題, 唔夠就真係差好遠. <br />\n<br />\n講真佢放粒 A12 都仲有可能好多人會諗一諗, 但係如果本身有以上呢啲問題, 見到仲要係 A13 就索性買返轉頭. 反正而家放 i11 Pro 都算係輸得最少嘅時間範圍之內."}]}